  "texts": [
    "It is imperative that educators and researchers understand the capabilities and limitations of this technology to maximize its benefits for students.",
    "This discussion delves into the current state of GenAI in education, addressing its potential, the challenges encountered in its application, and the future direction of research aimed at refining its utility in learning environments.GenAI has the potential to revolutionize education by providing personalized learning experiences, automating administrative tasks, and facilitating access to a wide range of information.",
    "Its ability to generate content based on input prompts can aid in the creation of customized learning materials, thereby catering to the diverse needs of students.",
    "This technology could serve as a powerful tool in guiding students to leverage resources more effectively and enhance their learning outcomes.However, our findings indicate that GenAI, when provided with limited prompts, tends to produce responses that are repetitive and often lack depth.",
    "This limitation highlights a significant challenge in its application within educational settings."
